author: Huawei
description: Is your connectivity built for the past or the future? Telcos' value is shifting from physical infrastructure to software-led flexibility. In a #Huawei #TransformTalks interview, Amy Cameron, Managing Director of Research for STL Partners, explains why harnessing AI's potential is non-negotiable for the survival of network providers: https://bit.ly/4q865KF #ThisIsHuawei
title: From Infrastructure to Intelligence: Telcos in the AI Era
